text: Aparajita Haque is a Bangladeshi politician who is elected as Member of 11th Jatiya Sangsad of Reserved Seats for Women. She is a politician of Bangladesh Awami League. Her father Khandaker Asaduzzaman was elected as an MP from Tangail-2. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Awami League politicians Category:People from Tangail District Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Women members of the Jatiya Sangsad Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
